{
  "name": "Empowered Bukijutsu",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-orange.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Taijutsu </p><p>You learn to empower your Bukijutsu with technique and refined skill, you gain the following benefits: </p><p>• When you cast a bukijutsu you can increase your [Weapons Damage] die by 1 step.  (d4&gt;d6&gt;d8&gt;d10&gt;d12) </p><p>• When a creature would make a saving throw to resist a bukijutsu you cast; If they fail by 5 or more, they take additional damage equal to the rank it was cast at (D- Rank: 4, C-Rank: 6, B-Rank: 8, A-Rank: 10, S-Rank: 12) </p><p>• When you would make a Constitution (Chakra control) check to maintain concentration on a Bukijutsu you cast, you can add 1d4 to the result of the check.</p><p></p>",
